## Docker Volumes

- `imagebuilder-cache` — SDK archives
- `ipk-cache` — downloaded packages
- `src-workdir` — OpenWrt source tree (persistent across builds)
- `src-dl-cache` — source download cache
- `src-ccache` — compiler cache
